-- Ecobank <ETI.LG> board removes CEO Tanoh - senior bank sources
-- By Matthew Mpoke Bigg
-- Tue Mar 11, 2014 11:24AM EDT
-- None



ACCRA, March 11 (Reuters) - The board of Ecobank <ETI.LG> decided on Tuesday to remove chief executive Thierry Tanoh following months of turmoil at one of the biggest financial institutions in sub-Saharan Africa.

